data.description: **ASSUMABLE VA LOAN at 3.25% - Call for more details** Welcome home to this spacious 5-bed, 2.5-bath gem with 2,293 sq ft of living space. Step inside to discover new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, a 2021 roof, and a 3-year-old HVAC system ensuring year-round comfort. The updated kitchen boasts granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Remodeled bathrooms add a touch of luxury. Plus, an above-ground pool for endless summer fun. The in-law suite over the large two-car garage makes the fifth bedroom perfect for guests or extended family. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
